{"word":"G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon - Beside","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sýn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beside</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Preposition / முன்னிடைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஓடு, உடன் - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"with, together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary preposition denoting <i>union</i>; <i>with</i> or <i>together</i> (but much closer than <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> or <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a>), that is, by association, companionship, process, resemblance, possession, instrumentality, addition, etc.<i>:</i> - beside, with. In compounds it has similar applications, including <i>completeness</i>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4776/4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800/4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806/4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832/4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833/4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854/4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855/4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862/4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880/4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891/4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916/4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957/4957\">G4957</a>"}]}